@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
title US-09 Generate Report (Current Code Reality)

actor Developer
participant "<u>reporter:ReportGenerator</u>" as TS
participant "<u>out:SystemFileIO</u>" as OUT

Developer -> TS: run demo_driver.py or pytest suites
activate TS
TS -> OUT: print SDR stats/results
TS --> Developer: textual outputs
deactivate TS

note over TS
No ReportGenerator or structured report API exists.
Reporting is manual via logs, prints, and test output.
end note
@enduml
